trans-unit.source: resolveSymbolicLinks uses the operating system's native file system API to resolve the path, using the realpath function on linux and OS X, and the GetFinalPathNameByHandle function on Windows. If the path does not point to an existing file system object, resolveSymbolicLinks throws a FileSystemException.
trans-unit.target: resolveSymbolicLinks使用操作系统的本机文件系统API来解析路径，在Linux和OS X上使用 realpath 函数，在Windows上使用 GetFinalPathNameByHandle 函数。如果路径未指向现有文件系统对象，则 resolveSymbolicLinks 抛出 FileSystemException 。

trans-unit.source: SendPorts are created from ReceivePorts. Any message sent through a SendPort is delivered to its corresponding ReceivePort. There might be many SendPorts for the same ReceivePort.
trans-unit.target: SendPort是从ReceivePort创建的。通过SendPort发送的任何消息都会传递到其相应的ReceivePort。相同的ReceivePort可能有许多SendPort。

trans-unit.source: SendPorts can be transmitted to other isolates, and they preserve equality when sent.
trans-unit.target: SendPort可以被传输到其他隔离，并且在发送时它们保持相等。
